      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine and transmission perform reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the interior is clean and smoke-free, the exterior shows some light wear, including a few minor stone chips and small door dings. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
