    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is ready for some serious TLC and is perfect for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone with the skills to bring it back to life. Grab this opportunity to own a diamond in the rough at a price that leaves plenty of room for your restoration dreams!",
